 each time, I could add it to `launchSettings.json` for IDE launches, create a shell alias, or use a `.env` file approach, though dotnet doesn't read those natively. Adding the property to the csproj file...","outputTokens":1206,"requestId":"A804:1618E9:267282E:28EBD55:6A0493B7"},"id":"ac40d438-3a29-403f-b199-9fec9a16f153","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:08:00.864Z","parentId":"2a23022d-e2e9-4570-8f40-2420c95b0912"}
